We are using MS project for managing this project. We think, it's great tool for this kind of project
From our WBS, we used MS project for scheduling each task, we also
Allocated and assignment resource to the right task
From that we estimated the project to cost around 800k for a duration of 247 days.
Which is close to the estimation obtain using basic organic COCOMO. That just increases our confidence
level about our estimations.

we're going to used scrum as software development process, As you can see from this graph a big chuck of the
schedule is consumed during implementation phase. implementation phase also include testing.
Since Security is a big concern for this application. We want
to make sure we did an exhaustive testing of the application before the final release.

We also guarantee  50 days worth of maintenance after the final release.
